---

<section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-nordic-surface relative overflow-hidden grain-overlay">
  <!-- Decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-nordic-border to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16 fade-in-section">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <span class="text-nordic-amber font-mono text-sm tracking-wider">01</span>
        <span class="w-12 h-px bg-nordic-border"></span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif italic text-nordic-text mb-4">
        About Me
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <!-- Main content - 3 columns -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-3 fade-in-section">
          <div class="prose prose-lg">
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-nordic-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-8 font-light">
              I'm an Engineering Team Lead at <a href="https://www.tomorrow.one" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-nordic-sky hover:text-nordic-amber transition-colors link-underline">Tomorrow</a>, where I help build financial products that people actually use.
            </p>

            <p class="text-nordic-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
              I split my time between writing code, unblocking my team, and trying to make banking less painful. I've been writing software and leading teams for a while now. These days I spend most of my time on architecture decisions, code reviews, and helping developers grow.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Skills as underlined text, not pills -->
          <div class="mt-10 pt-10 border-t border-nordic-border/50">
            <p class="text-sm text-nordic-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Areas of Focus</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-8 gap-y-3">
              <span class="skill-item text-nordic-text-secondary hover:text-nordic-amber transition-colors cursor-default">
                Team Leadership
              </span>
              <span class="skill-item text-nordic-text-secondary hover:text-nordic-sage transition-colors cursor-default">
                Software Engineering
              </span>
              <span class="skill-item text-nordic-text-secondary hover:text-nordic-lavender transition-colors cursor-default">
                FinTech
              </span>
              <span class="skill-item text-nordic-text-secondary hover:text-nordic-sky transition-colors cursor-default">
                System Design
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Info cards - 2 columns -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-4">
          <div class="stagger-item group">
            <div class="bg-nordic-card border border-nordic-border/50 p-6 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:border-nordic-amber/30 card-glow">
              <p class="text-xs text-nordic-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Current Role</p>
              <p class="text-nordic-text font-medium">Engineering Team Lead</p>
              <a href="https://www.tomorrow.one" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-nordic-sky text-sm hover:text-nordic-amber transition-colors link-underline">
                at Tomorrow
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="stagger-item group">
            <div class="bg-nordic-card border border-nordic-border/50 p-6 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:border-nordic-amber/30 card-glow">
              <p class="text-xs text-nordic-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Location</p>
              <p class="text-nordic-text font-medium">Lübeck, Germany</p>
              <p class="text-nordic-muted text-sm">Open to remote</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="stagger-item group">
            <div class="bg-nordic-card border border-nordic-border/50 p-6 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:border-nordic-amber/30 card-glow">
              <p class="text-xs text-nordic-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Education</p>
              <p class="text-nordic-text font-medium">M.Sc. Computer Science</p>
              <p class="text-nordic-muted text-sm">University of Lübeck</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .skill-item {
    position: relative;
  }

  .skill-item::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2px;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background: currentColor;
    opacity: 0.3;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .skill-item:hover::after {
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
</style>
